your life's purpose?

88
00:05:49.558 --> 00:05:51.526
Uh..

89
00:05:53.103 --> 00:05:55.606
Liberation is the purpose.

90
00:05:55.814 --> 00:05:57.737
It's a state of peace.

91
00:05:57.941 --> 00:06:00.865
A state of peace
that I-I was really

92
00:06:01.069 --> 00:06:05.119
really enjoying right up
until this very moment.

93
00:06:56.291 --> 00:06:57.838
Whoa. is he alright?

94
00:06:58.043 --> 00:06:59.260
He was just standing there.

95
00:06:59.461 --> 00:07:01.213
He just collapsed.

96
00:07:01.421 --> 00:07:03.048
Carter? Carter.

97
00:07:03.256 --> 00:07:04.098
He's not breathing.

98
00:07:04.299 --> 00:07:05.801
Carter? Carter. can you hear me?

99
00:07:10.138 --> 00:07:11.390
We had a. a deal.

100
