101
00:07:13.391 --> 00:07:16.019
You stay way away from me.
Forever.

102
00:07:16.227 --> 00:07:17.319
And that was my
every intention. Ritchie.

103
00:07:17.520 --> 00:07:19.113
No magic. no demons

104
00:07:19.314 --> 00:07:21.817
